						               													<description>You, as a criminal, will have to compete with other criminals (other players), in order to commit your assigned crimes and win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As the game proceeds, you must gather objects - items, that are described on your mission card. Once you've gathered the required items, then you will have to travel to the destination city, described on your mission card as well, and then try to commit your crime.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On your turn, you always have to travel towards a city. When you enter a city, you can draw an item card and interact with other criminals that you met inside the city, or in some other cases, you may interact with someone who is currently far away from you.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You can shoot another criminal, or hire a professional to do it. You can steal from another criminal, you can spy on them with your surveillance kit, you can use your anesthetic spray to immobilize them, you can force them to quit on their mission and get a new one, or you can set a trap for them. You can even get to drink with them in a bar, or fight them out in the streets.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The winner is the first one who will manage to complete a minimum of 3 missions. But this is up to you. The game is designed so that players may keep on playing for as long as they like and it allows a player to join in at any time!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
